ComicInfo.Title: West Town Story; Lionel's Lament; Situation Dichotomy; Formal Wear; Cabbage Patch Man; How To Squat; Waiting; American Dilemma; The History Of Health Insurance; The Cave Of Fear
ComicInfo.Summary:
West Town Story: A day in the life.
Lionel's Lament: The reason Lionel has to cook.
Situation Dichotomy: Billy is disturbed by his new neighbour.
Formal Wear: The elderly Mrs. Banks has few inhibitions.
Cabbage Patch Man: Where babies come from.
How To Squat: How to use squatter style toilets.
Waiting: The repetitive nature of waitressing.
American Dilemma: Dean is concerned that he's not heard back from Harvey Pekar about art samples.
The History Of Health Insurance: Chris has a new job.
The Cave Of Fear: A dangerous trip to some remote caves in Thailand.
